//i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F103421_c9372632ba90bc087008462f3d649ba3.jpg&h=0f2c8aec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以用極少既溶劑滴落紙樣辦度溶咗d 墨水，之後上面畀個電壓佢<br />\n溶劑連墨水就會因為電勢差直接進入質譜儀<br />\n簡單、方便、快捷<br />\n<br />\n透過PS-MS 除咗睇到墨水變質程度，更加可以分到唔同牌子既墨水</blockquote><br />\ntldr<br />\n講咁多墨水做乜 九成人都隨手執支筆就簽架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:07:10.000Z","msg":"無知真可怕<br />\n<br />\n人地做幾千萬生意自然會用私家筆<br />\n<br />\n得閒坐車去下中環睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747f13f92686bc19515b3096b33d94384a454a35","tid":508526,"uid":3324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"其實筆跡專家係讀邊科<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2e3f802902a0f96ff14abab831c63627e74e5f","tid":508526,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"求撚其咋嘛"},{"pid":"d17390ac84fea311ae68f961b25885dc9f50ad1b","tid":508526,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:18:44.000Z","msg":"咁點樣入行成為筆跡專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c88eff951cdf9fbb1666f6abce47df121bd4bd","tid":508526,"uid":153060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"scan上電腦用啲program嚟run<br />\n唔洗肉眼睇"},{"pid":"047b6d28d4dff71c9d9f63319cdb46a12e32eeb6","tid":508526,"uid":35315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35c88eff951cdf9fbb1666f6abce47df121bd4bd","tid":508526,"uid":153060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"scan上電腦用啲program嚟run<br />\n唔洗肉眼睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:29:39.000Z","msg":"前提要有依種專業去搵出所有分析嘅parameters<br />\n先可以program出個algorithm"},{"pid":"2ffc5de5e79c3f4ca1630281b5c0d98af07059f9","tid":508526,"uid":34213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:32:41.000Z","msg":"簽名可以算係有人嘅Dna響入面，獨特<br />\n除咗睇簽名仲可以睇手寫做對比，再細分筆觸<br />\n用儀器睇筆壓，左手定右手，向邊度剔/傾<br />\n<br />\n因為簽名有個人特色，所以外國冒簽個啲通常都180度反轉個名黎簽，廢事比人捉到signature<br />\n<br />\n中文簽名就唔知了"},{"pid":"ee6b42259d72ab4f01be70512b1ab70307d70a05","tid":508526,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d17390ac84fea311ae68f961b25885dc9f50ad1b","tid":508526,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:18:44.000Z","msg":"咁點樣入行成為筆跡專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:33:06.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb9fd20b71a849a48ca0cf0e587c2257b24e62a","tid":508526,"uid":158245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:34:57.000Z","msg":"每次簽都唔同，拎唔同筆簽仲差得遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3819fe38f3e81a406926a52933dfdde8fcdbe401","tid":508526,"uid":74277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:35:01.000Z","msg":"簽左份野可唔可以話唔係自己簽"},{"pid":"ff9b3104905e1043ed4fc668f4c7a13fd995054c","tid":508526,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3819fe38f3e81a406926a52933dfdde8fcdbe401","tid":508526,"uid":74277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:35:01.000Z","msg":"簽左份野可唔可以話唔係自己簽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T03:37:50.000Z","msg":"但係簽左唔係已經有法律效力架啦咩, 點樣可以話唔係自己簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecbfb5e34b02b045bdf8d73f311c3a06a1f42a7","tid":508526,"uid":49634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f37a7da265e35095c5814164e6e8981254689ad","tid":508526,"uid":135132,"like":167,"dislike":2,"score":165,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:54:32.000Z","msg":"根據當年小甜甜案報導，專家會搜集一定數量既簽名，分析每一劃用的力度分佈、轉彎角度、距離等等的共通點，去論證涉案簽名係唔係屬於呢個人。<br />\n<br />\n如果你每個簽名都唔同到搵唔到共通點，咁你個簽