n成班on9又話咩自己亂咁簽自己都唔識分乜乜柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己柒都要拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 低質到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3489b1fcf2907a13560210db39b3330193109488","tid":508526,"uid":55874,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:33:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地係度認真問緊一個職業點運作<br />\n成班on9又話咩自己亂咁簽自己都唔識分乜乜柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己柒都要拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 低質到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲公屋𡃁仔質素係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a242ee3c8a796a18f48fe7c3404f2641a0e6dca","tid":508526,"uid":19728,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>順帶一提，認簽名仲可以睇下d 墨水<br />\n<br />\n樓上講到話睇簽名同食家一樣主觀9up真係膠都費事俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多時生意佬往往都係用同一枝筆簽名，只refill墨水<br />\n<br />\n所以係可以用驗墨水既形式<br />\n<br />\n首先<span style=\"color: red;\">唔同筆既墨水都係由唔同既顏料撈埋</span><br />\n<br />\n可以用thin-layer chromatography (TLC)去分離唔同既成份<br />\n(有少少似大家細個上初中科學堂玩既Paper Chromatography 實驗，一滴M&amp;M 朱古力既外層顏料都可以分成幾隻野）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/103025_d92c9ae4f90281d8fc9e9b366b15ab53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F103025_d92c9ae4f90281d8fc9e9b366b15ab53.jpg&h=62479bee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁比較返文件被書寫既唔同位置上既墨水，如果係由唔同既筆所寫，就可以判斷特定位置係唔係後來先加上去<br />\n(甚至乎只係喺銀碼上加筆令1 變 7 都睇得到）<br />\n<br />\n另外比對法證實驗室儲存既各款墨水喺TLC 既表現，甚至係可以知道寫果個人用咩筆；依個時候要比較下枝筆既歷史，例如一份1999年生效既聲明如果係用2001年先至推出市場既筆嚟寫既話，成份聲明都一定係虛假文書<br />\n<br />\n咁再進階少少，當墨水已經寫咗喺紙上面之後就會曝露於空氣同光線中，成份會隨住時間而慢慢變質，部份既墨水分子會變成比較細既分子<br />\n<br />\n我用最普遍既藍原子筆為例<br />\n都會含有染料<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/103251_9e74af6f0bf1077f4ce2dc9e253c4afc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F103251_9e74af6f0bf1077f4ce2dc9e253c4afc.jpg&h=586105e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁喺變質過程當中，分子既 -CH2CH3 會被氫(-H)所取代<br />\n<br />\n即係喺同一粉分子裏面，一個group被取代既話，分子質量會降低28；兩個既話就係56<br />\n<br />\n因應以上既現象，即使係用同一款筆去寫，只要一經質譜儀去量度，就可以有效咁分到個簽名係本身已經有定係新簽上去<br />\n<br />\n咁講多少少，驗問題文件既一個難點係盡可能唔可以破壞文件既整存性<br />\n<br />\n所以即使要做破壞性既化學測試，亦只可以用一種特製既工具，好似釘窿機咁開個洞，攞少少樣辦出嚟<br />\n(個洞仲細過原子筆筆尖)<br />\n<br />\n要用咁少既樣辦做檢測，唔會好似一般檢測咁用GC<br />\n<br />\n現代有直接少少既paper spray mass spectrometer (PS-MS)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/103421_c9372632ba90bc087008462f3d649ba3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F103421_c9372632ba90bc087008462f3d649ba3.jpg&h=0f2c8aec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以用極少既溶劑滴落紙樣辦度溶咗d 墨水，之後上面畀個電壓佢<br />\n溶劑連墨水就會因為電勢差直接進入質譜儀<br />\n簡單、方便、快捷<br />\n<br />\n透過PS-MS 除咗睇到墨水變質程度，更加可以分到唔同牌子既墨水</blockquote><br />\ntldr<br />\n講咁多墨水做乜 九成人都隨手執支筆就簽架啦</blockquote><br />\n出少句聲冇人話你啞架柒頭"},{"pid":"ebd2e067bf72c817a01cfc9118f46e29c9a00cf4","tid":508526,"uid":19728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地係度認真問緊一個職業點運作<br />\n成班on9又話咩自己亂咁簽自己都唔識分乜乜柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己柒都要拎出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 低質到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家多咗小學雞係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ed93569b1e83c430d95c776ce0b0170406e0bf","tid":508526,"uid":129169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a242ee3c8a796a18f48fe7c3404f2641a0e6dca","tid":508526,"uid":19728,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>順帶一提，認簽名仲可以睇下d 墨水<br />\n<br />\n樓上講到話睇簽名同食家一樣主觀9up真係膠都費事俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多時生意佬往往都係用同一枝筆簽名，只refill墨水<br />\n<br />\n所以係可以用驗墨水既形式<br />\n<br />\n首先<span style=\"color: red;\">唔同筆既墨水都係由唔同既顏料撈埋</span><br />\n<br />\n可以用thin-layer chromatography (TLC)去分離唔同既成份<br />\n(有少少似大家細個上初中科學堂玩既Paper Chromatography 實驗，一滴M&amp;M 朱古力既外層顏料都可以分成幾隻野）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/103025_d92c9ae4f90281d8fc9e9b366b15ab53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F103025_d92c9ae4f90281d8fc9e9b366b15ab53.jpg&h=62479bee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁比較返文件被書寫既唔同位置上既墨水，如果係由唔同既筆所寫，就可以判斷特定位置係唔係後來先加上去<br />\n(甚至乎只係喺銀碼上加筆令1 變 7 都睇得到）<br />\n<br />\n另外比對法證實驗室儲存既各款墨水喺TLC 既表現，甚至係可以知道寫果個人用咩筆；依個時候要比較下枝筆既歷史，例如一份1999年生效既聲明如果係